{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "花如玉向风四娘和沈璧君声称萧十一郎抢走了他的未婚妻冰冰，为证明此事，他将二人带往姑苏大亨楼。风四娘被制住穴道，沈璧君蒙面同行。大亨楼内富豪云集，柳苏州携美妻炫富，保镖高刚随侍。萧十一郎以全新华丽形象登场，身旁伴有绝色丽人冰冰，与昔日不修边幅的模样判若两人。沈璧君见冰冰美若天人，心沉如铁，暗自落泪。冰冰看中柳苏州妻的翠玉耳环，萧十一郎与柳苏州发生冲突，高刚拔剑相向，却被萧十一郎一弹断剑，惊骇失色。萧十一郎亮出身份，气势震慑全场。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为他抢了我的女人，所以我也要抢他的女人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "他抢去了你的什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他抢去了我的冰冰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "冰冰是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "冰冰就是我的表妹，也是我的未婚妻子。但那萧十一郎却仗着他的武功比我高，仗着他比我更有钱，竟将我的冰冰抢走了，连看都不许别人多看一眼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "谢天石就因为多看了她两眼，所以眼睛才会瞎的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你们若以为他对你们好，你们就错了，他对冰冰才是真的好，为了冰冰，他什么事都肯做，冰冰若要他挖出你们的眼珠子来，他也不会拒绝的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "我不信，你说的话我连一个字也不信。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你是真的不信，还是不敢相信、不忍相信？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "我死也不相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "看来你真是个痴心的女人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "我以前也冤枉过他的，但现在我已知道，他绝不会是这种人，绝不会做这种事的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他以前也许不是这种人，但每个人都会变的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "不管你怎么说，我还是不信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我若能证明，你又怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "只要你能证明他真的做了这种事，你随便对我怎么样都没关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我若能证明，你就肯嫁给我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "我说过，随你对我怎样都没关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你说过的话，算不算数？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "我虽然是个女人，却从来也没有做过言而无信的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好，我信任你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "你准备怎么样证明给她看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我准备让她自己去看看萧十一郎和冰冰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "到哪里去看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "大亨楼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "大亨楼是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是个花钱的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "萧十一郎在那里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这几天他一定在姑苏附近，只要他在附近，就一定会去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为他现在是个大亨，若是不带着他那个如花似玉的美人儿到大亨楼去亮亮相，岂非白到了苏州一趟？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "你也想带我们去亮亮相？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只要你们肯答应我一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你们可以张大了眼睛去看，却不能张嘴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为你们若是一出声，就什么也看不见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "好，我答应你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你真的能一直闭着嘴不出声？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "你以为我是个什么样的女人？是个多嘴婆？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你当然不是多嘴婆，但我却还是不相信你会真的那么老实。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "你连自己的老婆都不信任，你还能相信谁？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "一个男人若是太信任自己的老婆，他一定是个笨蛋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "杨开泰就是个笨蛋，否则又怎么会让你溜走？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "他并不是个笨蛋，只不过是个君子而已。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "但我却既不是笨蛋，也不是君子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "所以你已决定不信任我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我可以信任她，我知道她是很老实的女人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "我不老实？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这屋子里老实人好像只有她一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "那么你准备怎么样？把我的嘴缝起来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只缝你的嘴也没有用，你说不定会翻跟斗的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "你……你……准备用什么法子来对付我？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我会想出个好法子来的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只要他到了姑苏附近，就一定会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你怎么知道他会到姑苏附近来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜的",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那边还有张靠窗的桌子，大爷先在那里坐下来，小人去泡壶好茶。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你看这副耳环怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "还不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我喜欢它的颜色。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你喜欢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shao_nu",
      "text": "我很喜欢，却不知这位姑娘肯不肯让给我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
